All ref images have to be the same resolution.
Though image list can maintain resolution for each ref image but ComfyUI will run multiple times.
Use padding and target (height) resolution to control the size of the subject relative to the image. In theory, the bigger the subject relative to the image, the better the result.

properties.Node name for S&R: workflow>🐉 JK::Image Crop by Mask and Resize

widgets_values:
VACE reference image can be the same as the common ref image generated based on the video first frame. However, it can be more complicated using 1 to 3 reference images, including main subjects with a white background and/or background image, batch/concatenate them as one image grid with/without scaling them to the project/video resolution.

1. Build your reference images yourself using 1-3 images based on the need.
2. Link the chosen one (brown color) to the Setter.
